Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Conveniently located near Lamar Avenue (Hwy 78) and Shelby Drive.  Easy access to the Memphis International Airport, FedEx & UPS Hubs and BNSF Intermodal yard.

2021 Latham is strategically located in the Belz Industrial Park, one of the largest and most well-positioned industrial parks in Memphis. The Property features convenient accessibility to the Memphis International Airport, FedEx and UPS hubs, the Port of Memphis, the Canadian National Rail as well as major traffic arteries including I-55, I-40, and I-240.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to present for sublease 2021 Latham Street, Memphis, TN. The free-standing manufacturing/warehouse facility contains approximately 93,300 SF and is leased through August 2022.
